    "To be precise, LLM Top K reached 87.6% accuracy with 10-shot learning, and the model fine-tuned on 70 instances achieved 94.9% accuracy.",
    "Thus, we claim that fine-tuning further boosts the GPT's capability in DDoS attack detection, even though it requires more training data to surpass the performance of a few-shot learning model.",
